        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Cost Breakdown and Pricing Model"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The pricing model is usage-based, charged per character processed, with discounts for high-volume commitments. The base rate is $15 per million characters for the Qwen3 TTS 12Hz 1.7B model, with additional fees for custom voice cloning setup (one-time $50 per voice). There are no upfront costs, and billing is monthly."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To optimize costs, consider these factors:"
